♪ Oh Bonny Portmore

1016
01:32:12,071 --> 01:32:15,907
♪ I am sorry to see

1017
01:32:16,742 --> 01:32:22,038
♪ Such a woeful destruction

1018
01:32:22,164 --> 01:32:26,626
♪ Of your ornament tree

1019
01:32:26,752 --> 01:32:31,422
♪ For it stood on your shore

1020
01:32:31,549 --> 01:32:36,177
♪ For many's the long day

1021
01:32:36,303 --> 01:32:42,725
♪ 'Til the long boats from Antrim

1022
01:32:42,851 --> 01:32:49,190
♪ Came to float it away...

1023
01:32:50,442 --> 01:32:52,860
(Wind blowing)

1024
01:33:39,742 --> 01:33:43,077
So, why are you here?
You hoping you'd find me?

1025
01:33:46,457 --> 01:33:48,791
For whatever reason,
Kell made his choice.

1026
01:33:53,297 --> 01:33:54,797
So...

1027
01:33:55,674 --> 01:33:57,258
...what now?

1028
01:34:00,346 --> 01:34:02,388
Trust.

1029
01:34:02,514 --> 01:34:04,015
You can always trust me, Faith.

1030
01:34:05,017 --> 01:34:06,851
Faith is dead.

1031
01:34:07,811 --> 01:34:11,648
I thought we'd give
Kate another chance.

1032
01:34:22,534 --> 01:34:24,494
Not yet.

1033
01:34:24,620 --> 01:34:26,329
(Kate whispers)
'Till the day we are reborn. '

1034
01:34:26,455 --> 01:34:28,081
You hold onto it for me.

1035
01:34:29,458 --> 01:34:30,917
We've got plenty of time.

